m/review/527310/monster-hunter-wilds-review-pc-ps5-xbox\"\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e, Capcom will still charge you money to \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/monster-hunter-wilds-guide/529492/how-to-change-appearance-edit-vouchers-hunter-palico\"\u003eedit your character\u003c/a\u003e or Palico more than once.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOnce you create your character during the intro sequence, you’ll only have one opportunity to fully change them using a free character edit voucher. After that, it’ll cost you at least \u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701642\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F3289620%2FMonster_Hunter_Wilds__Character_Edit_Voucher_ThreeVoucher_Pack%2F%3Fcurator_clanid%3D44795648\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003e$6.99\u003c/a\u003e to even enter the customization menu again — although that’ll net you three vouchers. \u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701642\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F3336850%2FMonster_Hunter_Wilds__Palico_Edit_Voucher_ThreeVoucher_Pack%2F%3Fcurator_clanid%3D44795648\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003ePalico edit vouchers\u003c/a\u003e are the same deal, but you can also buy a three-pack of both for \u003ca href=\"https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701642\u0026amp;xs=1\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F3336890%2FMonster_Hunter_Wilds__Character__Palico_Edit_Voucher_ThreeVoucher_Pack%2F%3Fcurator_clanid%3D44795648\" rel=\"sponsored\"\u003e$9.99\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere’s currently no way to earn character or Palico edit vouchers by simply playing the game, just as it is in \u003cem\u003eMonster Hunter Rise \u003c/em\u003eand\u003cem\u003e Monster Hunter World.\u003c/em\u003e In your tent, you can edit minor aspects of your character without a voucher, like their makeup, facial hair, and clothing, but everything else is locked behind the full customization menu.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image showing Yoru in the character editor in Monster Hunter Wilds.\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/Monster-Hunter-Wilds-Guides-Ana_2025-02-28_12-35-25.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u002